```

### 6.3 Firestore Indexes

The project defines composite indexes in [firestore.indexes.json](file:///c:/metallic-oort/firestore.indexes.json):

| Collection | Fields | Purpose |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| `tripHistory` | `timestamp DESC` | Sort trips by recency |
| `tripHistory` | `date ASC, timestamp DESC` | Daily trip queries |
| `tripHistory` | `driverId ASC, timestamp DESC` | Driver-specific history |
| `users` | `createdAt DESC` | Sort users by creation date |
| `destinations` | `isActive ASC, name ASC` | Active destinations sorted by name |
| `destinations` | `createdAt DESC` | Sort destinations by creation date |

