## 7. APIs & External Services

### 7.1 OpenStreetMap Tile API

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **URL Pattern** | `https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png` |
| **Purpose** | Map tile images for Leaflet |
| **Cost** | Free (open source) |
| **Caching** | CacheFirst strategy via Service Worker (30-day max) |

### 7.2 Nominatim Geocoding API

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Base URL** | `https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org/search` |
| **Purpose** | Address search + reverse geocoding |
| **Cost** | Free (no API key required) |
| **Rate Limit** | 1 request/second (honored via debounce) |
| **Region Bias** | Gujarat bounding box (`68.1,20.1,74.5,24.7`) |
| **User-Agent** | `UniTrack-CampusBusTracker/1.0` (required by policy) |

**Features used:**
- Forward geocoding (address → coordinates) for route building
- Reverse geocoding (coordinates → address) for stop naming
- Gujarat region bias for locally relevant results

### 7.3 Web Geolocation API (Browser Native)

```javascript
navigator.geolocation.watchPosition(successCallback, errorCallback, {
    enableHighAccuracy: true,  // Uses GPS hardware
    maximumAge: 3000,          // Accept 3s old positions
    timeout: 15000             // Wait up to 15s for fix
});
```

### 7.4 Firebase SDK APIs

| SDK Module | Functions Used |
|-----------|---------------|
| `firebase/auth` | `signInWithEmailAndPassword`, `createUserWithEmailAndPassword`, `onAuthStateChanged`, `signOut`, `sendPasswordResetEmail` |
| `firebase/firestore` | `collection`, `doc`, `getDocs`, `getDoc`, `addDoc`, `setDoc`, `updateDoc`, `deleteDoc`, `query`, `where`, `orderBy`, `limit`, `serverTimestamp` |
| `firebase/database` | `ref`, `set`, `onValue`, `onDisconnect` |
| `firebase/app` | `initializeApp`, `getApps`, `deleteApp` |

