## 16. Data Flow Diagrams

### 16.1 Complete Data Flow — Driver to Student

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Driver (Mobile)
    participant GPS as Device GPS
    participant RTDB as Firebase RTDB
    participant FS as Cloud Firestore
    participant S as Student (Browser)
    participant M as Leaflet Map

    Note over D,S: Driver Goes Online
    D->>FS: Fetch today's schedule (Firestore)
    FS-->>D: Schedule with route, bus, shift
    D->>RTDB: set('driverStatus/{uid}', {isOnDuty: true})
    D->>GPS: watchPosition() starts

    Note over D,S: Continuous Tracking
    loop Every GPS Update (~3s)
        GPS-->>D: Position {lat, lng, speed, heading}
        D->>RTDB: set('busLocations/{uid}', locationData)
        RTDB-->>S: onValue() → push update
        S->>M: Update marker position
    end

    Note over D,S: Student Filters
    S->>FS: Fetch routes (one-time)
    FS-->>S: Route list with stops & polylines
    S->>M: Draw route polyline on map

    Note over D,S: Driver Goes Offline
    D->>RTDB: set('busLocations/{uid}', {isActive: false})
    D->>RTDB: set('driverStatus/{uid}', {isOnDuty: false})
    RTDB-->>S: Bus marker disappears from map
```

### 16.2 Admin — User Creation Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin
    participant P as Primary Auth
    participant S as Secondary Auth
    participant FS as Cloud Firestore

    A->>A: Fill user form (name, role, birthday)
    A->>A: Generate email (rollNo@gnu.ac.in)
    A->>A: Generate password (birthday DDMMYYYY)
    A->>S: createUserWithEmailAndPassword(secondaryAuth)
    S-->>A: New user UID
    A->>S: signOut(secondaryAuth) immediately
    A->>FS: setDoc('users/{uid}', profileData)
    A->>A: deleteApp(secondaryApp)
    Note over A,P: Admin remains signed in on Primary Auth!
```

