## 20. Network Requirements & Data Usage

### 20.1 Bandwidth Requirements

| Feature | Data Usage | Direction |
|---------|-----------|-----------|
| **Map Tiles** | ~50-200 KB per tile | Download (cached after first load) |
| **GPS Update (Driver)** | ~200-500 bytes per write | Upload |
| **GPS Subscription (Student)** | ~200-500 bytes per push event | Download |
| **Firestore Query** | ~1-5 KB per document | Download |
| **Firebase Auth** | ~2-5 KB per request | Both |
| **Geocoding Search** | ~1-3 KB per request | Download |

### 20.2 Estimated Daily Data Usage

| User Role | Estimated Daily Data | Breakdown |
|-----------|---------------------|-----------|
| **Driver** (8-hour shift) | ~5-10 MB | GPS uploads + map tiles |
| **Student** (30 min tracking) | ~2-5 MB | Map tiles + live bus updates |
| **Admin** (panel usage) | ~10-20 MB | Dashboard data + map tiles |

### 20.3 Network Protocols Used

| Protocol | Where | Purpose |
|----------|-------|---------|
| **HTTPS** | All Firebase SDK calls | Encrypted API communication |
| **WSS (WebSocket Secure)** | Firebase RTDB | Real-time GPS streaming |
| **HTTPS** | OpenStreetMap tiles | Map imagery download |
| **HTTPS** | Nominatim API | Geocoding requests |

### 20.4 Offline Behavior

| Feature | Offline Behavior |
|---------|-----------------|
| **Map** | Shows previously cached tiles (up to 500 tiles via Service Worker) |
| **GPS Tracking (Driver)** | Continues tracking, queues updates in `localStorage` |
| **Bus Locations (Student)** | Shows last known positions, "Offline" indicator appears |
| **Login** | Not possible (requires Firebase Auth server) |
| **Admin CRUD** | Not possible (requires Firestore connection) |

