## 26. Trip History & Analytics

### 26.1 Event Logging

Every driver check-in and check-out creates a [trip history](file:///c:/metallic-oort/client/src/services/tripHistory.js) record:

```javascript
{
    driverId: "uid-123",
    driverName: "Rajesh Kumar",
    eventType: "check_in",           // or "check_out"
    busId: "bus-doc-id",
    routeId: "route-doc-id",
    routeName: "Ahmedabad Express",
    scheduleId: "schedule-doc-id",
    timestamp: "2025-01-15T08:30:00.000Z",
    date: "2025-01-15",
    location: { lat: 23.529, lng: 72.457 }
}
```

### 26.2 Analytics Computed from Trip History

| Metric | Calculation |
|--------|------------|
| **Daily Check-ins** | Count of `eventType === 'check_in'` for a given date |
| **Daily Check-outs** | Count of `eventType === 'check_out'` for a given date |
| **Active Trips** | `checkIns - checkOuts` (currently running) |
| **Unique Drivers Today** | `new Set(trips.map(t => t.driverId)).size` |
| **Unique Routes Today** | `new Set(trips.map(t => t.routeId)).size` |
| **Weekly Summary** | Last 7 days of daily stats (used for admin chart) |

