### Complete List of All Custom hooks

| Hook | File | Data Source | Purpose |
|------|------|-------------|---------|
| `useAuth()` | `contexts/AuthContext.jsx` | Firebase Auth + Firestore | Global auth state, user role |
| `useBusLocations()` | `track/hooks/useBusLocations.js` | Firebase RTDB | Real-time bus positions |
| `useUserLocation()` | `track/hooks/useUserLocation.js` | Capacitor Geolocation | Student's own GPS location |
| `useRoutes()` | `track/hooks/useRoutes.js` | Firestore | Fetch active routes |
| `useFavorites()` | `track/hooks/useFavorites.js` | localStorage | Persist favorite routes |
| `useDriverTracking()` | `driver/hooks/useDriverTracking.js` | Geolocation + RTDB | GPS broadcasting, offline queue |
| `useDriverSchedule()` | `driver/hooks/useDriverSchedule.js` | Firestore + RTDB | Today's schedule, check-in/out |
| `useScheduleData()` | `hooks/useScheduleData.js` | Firestore | Admin schedule management |
| `useDashboardStats()` | `hooks/useDashboardStats.js` | Firestore | Admin dashboard counters |
| `useAnalyticsData()` | `hooks/useAnalyticsData.js` | Firestore (tripHistory) | Weekly chart data |
| `useUsersData()` | `hooks/useUsersData.js` | Firestore | User list with filtering |
| `usePWAInstall()` | `hooks/usePWAInstall.js` | Browser Events | PWA install prompt |

