### Complete Service Layer Reference

| Service | File | Methods | CRUD Target |
|---------|------|---------|-------------|
| Firebase Init | `firebase.js` | `getSecondaryAuth()` | Firebase app instances |
| Auth | `auth.js` | `signIn`, `signOut`, `resetPassword` | Firebase Auth |
| Database (Generic) | `database.js` | `create`, `read`, `update`, `delete`, `getAll` | Any Firestore collection |
| Users | `users.js` | `getAll`, `getById`, `update`, `delete` | `users` collection |
| User Creation | `userCreation.js` | `createSingleUser`, `validateUserData`, `checkEmailExists` | `users` + Firebase Auth |
| Bulk Import | `bulkImport.js` | `bulkCreateUsers`, `validateBulkData`, `generateErrorReport` | Batch `users` creation |
| Excel Parser | `excelParser.js` | `parseExcelFile`, `downloadTemplate` | Client-side file parsing |
| Destinations | `destinations.js` | `getAll`, `create`, `update`, `delete` | `destinations` collection |
| Geocoding | `geocoding.js` | `searchAddress`, `reverseGeocode` | Nominatim API |
| Schedule Templates | `scheduleTemplates.js` | `getAll`, `create`, `update`, `delete`, `generateDates`, `generateScheduleEntries` | `scheduleTemplates` collection |
| Trip History | `tripHistory.js` | `logTripEvent`, `getTripHistory`, `getDailyStats`, `getWeeklySummary` | `tripHistory` collection |
